name: Rotation of Comet Nuclei: Table 1
abstract: This collection presents Table 1 of Samarasinha, et al. (2004): 'Information on spin states of specific comets', as published in 'Comets II' (Festou, Keller and Weaver, eds.). These data were migrated from the PDS3 dataset and EAR-C-COMPIL-5-COMET-NUC-ROTATION-V1.0, Rotation of Comet Nuclei: Table 1.
citation: Samarasinha, N.H., Mueller B.E.A., Belton, M.J.S., and Jorda, L., Rotation of Comet Nuclei: Table 1 (PDS4 Format), urn:nasa:pds:compil-comet:nuc_rotation::1.0, NASA Planetary Data System, 2019.
